  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Start your day with a buffet breakfast in the panoramic dining room. Choose between pastries, cakes, local bread from the bakery, homemade jams, yogurts,  meats and cheeses, and freshly prepared egg dishes.</p>
<p>You'll get a choice of four courses for dinner with local and international dishes available. There's a weekly Tyrolean dinner and a great wine list to complement your meal.</p>
<p>Complimentary tea and cake is served every day between 3pm and 5pm.  </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
